graph TB
    subgraph "Model Registry Operator"
        ControllerManager[Controller Manager<br/>Reconciles ModelRegistry CRs]
        WebhookService[Webhook Service<br/>Validates/Mutates CRs]
        MetricsService[Metrics Service<br/>Prometheus Endpoint]

        ControllerManager -->|exposes| MetricsService
        ControllerManager -->|uses| WebhookService
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        ModelRegistryV1Beta1[ModelRegistry v1beta1<br/>Current API]
        ModelRegistryV1Alpha1[ModelRegistry v1alpha1<br/>Deprecated]

        ModelRegistryV1Alpha1 -.->|conversion webhook| ModelRegistryV1Beta1
    end

    subgraph "Deployed Model Registry Instance"
        Deployment[model-registry Deployment]
        RESTContainer[REST Container<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]
        OAuthProxyContainer[OAuth Proxy Container<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
        Service[model-registry Service<br/>ClusterIP]
        Route[OpenShift Route<br/>External Access]

        Deployment -->|contains| RESTContainer
        Deployment -->|contains optional| OAuthProxyContainer
        Service -->|exposes| Deployment
        Route -.->|optional| Service
    end

    User[User/Admin] -->|creates| ModelRegistryV1Beta1
    ModelRegistryV1Beta1 -->|watched by| ControllerManager
    ControllerManager -->|creates| Deployment
    ControllerManager -->|creates| Service
    ControllerManager -->|creates| Route

    RESTContainer -->|connects to| Database[(PostgreSQL/MySQL<br/>ML Metadata Storage)]
    OAuthProxyContainer -->|forwards to| RESTContainer
    OAuthProxyContainer -->|authenticates via| OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server]

    ControllerManager -->|watches| PlatformCR[components.platform.opendatahub.io<br/>modelregistries]
    ControllerManager -->|uses| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]

    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes| MetricsService

    style ControllerManager fill:#4a90e2
    style WebhookService fill:#4a90e2
    style MetricsService fill:#4a90e2
    style ModelRegistryV1Beta1 fill:#f5a623
    style ModelRegistryV1Alpha1 fill:#999
    style RESTContainer fill:#7ed321
    style OAuthProxyContainer fill:#7ed321
    style Database fill:#e8e8e8
    style OAuthServer fill:#e8e8e8
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8
    style PlatformCR fill:#f5a623
